description:
What is the most difficult element in driving a car? parking? you are absolutely right.
In our game you will be able to improve your parking skill. In the game you will be able to find many parking options with varying degrees of difficulty. You can also ride on different cars from ordinary to supercars.Will you be able to complete the entire task and deliver the cars and park all of our cars without a single mistake?


GAME FEATURES:
♦ Very detailed car models
♦ Large selection of transport
♦ Realistic car controller
♦ Large assortment of differents levels
♦ 3 modes that differ in difficulty
name: Car Parking Madness School Drive Mechanic Car Games Simulator 2023
